00:10:10.780 --> 00:10:12.000
three things have happened.

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:13.820
And I'm using Chinese factories
as one example,

00:10:13.820 --> 00:10:15.240
though it extends beyond them.

00:10:15.240 --> 00:10:17.150
Three things have happened
to Chinese factories.

00:10:17.150 --> 00:10:18.415
First of all, the
web generation

00:10:18.415 --> 00:10:19.400
has come into power.

00:10:19.400 --> 00:10:20.650
They get it.

00:10:22.760 --> 00:10:25.070
Opening a web interface is
the right way to work.

00:10:25.070 --> 00:10:27.860
Number two, their own
manufacturing systems are

00:10:27.860 --> 00:10:30.000
increasingly robotic and
automated, which means they

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:30.970
are very flexible.

00:10:30.970 --> 00:10:32.090
They can make small batches.

00:10:32.090 --> 00:10:33.890
And they can change the
design very quickly.

00:10:33.890 --> 00:10:36.890
And number three, they realized
that serving small

00:10:36.890 --> 00:10:40.670
batches, serving a niche
interest actually is a higher

00:10:40.670 --> 00:10:41.380
margin business.

00:10:41.380 --> 00:10:44.570
That's the way they get out of
the commodity trap is by

00:10:44.570 --> 00:10:47.500
