00:24:14.570 --> 00:24:17.610
That's part of the fun is just
listening to the explanations

00:24:17.610 --> 00:24:19.200
of why things have
been delayed.

00:24:19.200 --> 00:24:21.330
Very educational into the
learning process of

00:24:21.330 --> 00:24:23.180
manufacturing.

