skill.

00:58:03.060 --> 00:58:05.800
So it's going to end up in
curriculums and making it free

00:58:05.800 --> 00:58:07.620
on Android and DEWA.

00:58:07.620 --> 00:58:09.310
Actually, they're on
IOS at the moment.

00:58:09.310 --> 00:58:10.700
But anyway, Autodesk
is a good choice.

00:58:10.700 --> 00:58:11.860
3D Systems is doing good work.

00:58:11.860 --> 00:58:12.815
MakerBot is not public.

00:58:12.815 --> 00:58:14.280
You can't invest in
it at the moment.

00:58:14.280 --> 00:58:16.260
But they're obviously doing
good work as well.

00:58:18.970 --> 00:58:21.740
We also used Cellworks and
a couple of others.

00:58:21.740 --> 00:58:26.330
But I would say buying Autodesk
