01:00:29.530 --> 01:00:31.480
CHRIS ANDERSON: I would say
that we're looking--

01:00:31.480 --> 01:00:33.950
I would look at full color 3D
printing within five years on

01:00:33.950 --> 01:00:37.640
the desktop and multi-material,
including

01:00:37.640 --> 01:00:40.534
electrical circuitry, within
seven to eight.

01:00:40.534 --> 01:00:41.330
MALE SPEAKER: Thank you.

